{"tid":862649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「如果我是日本人也侵略中國」 鬥魚主播遭封殺！","createTime":"2018-10-15T03:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T04:18:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"577ab3ff8f95c1dad91fe63ee92e09d39977d1e9","tid":862649,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539428793_9a59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539428793_9a59.jpg&h=35358105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內網民爆料稱，鬥魚主播「B總001」近日在直播時大放厥詞，該主播揚言稱：「從進化論的角度來說，中國人沒有日韓進化得好；如果我是日本人，我也選擇侵略中國。」<br />\n<br />\n言論一出，該主播立即遭到網民聲討。網友紛紛指斥，應該封殺這種沒有底線的無良主播。據了解該主播此前就因公開辱罵他人，直播中瘋狂爆粗遭到過多次舉報。<br />\n<br />\n目前，「B總001」的鬥魚直播已被平台關閉。不過他本人以及鬥魚平台均未對此事發表任何聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181013/58791404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F58791404&d=unlMM%2FuKD%2FK3TerAu3X8VNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=39302205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F58791404&h=0e06ea96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181013/58791404</a>"},{"pid":"a1b7e90086f3466dcb259a9da8e85b9178c40684","tid":862649,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49ed98150df6aba4b2afb21ffa89e29a90069319","tid":862649,"uid":63909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"從進化論的角度來說，中國人沒有日韓進化得好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6660a1dc76e3b541cdceaf03199871dadc9a82c8","tid":862649,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"reply